posting_body: ['Looking for a pet-friendly apartment community in San Mateo, CA?', 'Then look no further than Mode Apartments as we proudly accept cats and dogs.', 'Now your pet can relax by your\xa0 side and enjoy the comforts of your new apartment home.', 'Call now for details!', 'This two bedroom two bathroom apartment features a fully equipped kitchen, coat closet, washer/dryer, walk-in closets, ensuite bathrooms, and a patio/balcony!', 'This apartment requires a $750 deposit.', 'MODE, managed by Sares-Regis Group', '2089 Pacific Blvd., Ste A', 'San Mateo, CA 94403', 'show contact info', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Community Features', '* After-Hours Emergency Maintenance', '* Minutes from Restaurants, Shopping, and Much More', '* Elevator', '* Bike Racks', '* Controlled Access', '*', "Our prices can change daily, price listed is based on today's availability.", 'Call for details.', '* TV Lounge', '* E-Lounge', '* Community Kitchen', '* Package Acceptance', '* Easy Freeway Access', '* Short or Long Term Lease Available', '* Landscaped Courtyards', '* Yoga Lounge', '* Bark Park', '* Fitness Studio', '* Easy Access to Public Transportation', '* Garage Parking', '* Community Lounge', '* Credit Cards Accepted', '* Outdoor Grill Area', '* EV Charging', '* Extra Storage', '* Renters Insurance is Required', '* Professionally Managed']
